comments.comment: <denchmark-link:https://github.com/danmane>@danmane</denchmark-link> : Do you know what the issue is here?

But it should be: <denchmark-link:https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.7/api_docs/cc/ClassEnv.html>https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.7/api_docs/cc/ClassEnv.html</denchmark-link>
